description: On this episode of The CouRage and Nadeshot Show presented by Cash App, CouRage and Nadeshot welcome on streamer and new father, TimtheTatman. They discuss the DrDisrespect ban on Twitch, favorite anime moments, being a father, Overwatch League, and more!
